Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZTSICODEND From W1CHGITG
Return

$AV_ZTSICODEND
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"ATABDIV","LNGDES",num$(indice+20),num$([M]TSICODEND(indice))) From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
